vested\nover the system to trigger a duplication event is around $\\sim 10^{-13}{\\rm\nJ}$. Without aiming to describe a truly biological process of duplication, this\ntheoretical contribution seeks to explicitly define and identify the key actors\nthat participate in it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2018 10:34:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2018 20:34:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-07"}
