e interior critical zero points of\n$u$ is less than or equal to the half of the number of its isolated zero points\non the boundaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2018 15:02:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-13"}
